text: Experience the tranquility of country living with this custom-built home nestled on 10 gently sloped acres that boast mountain views. With just under 3000 sq ft of living space, this beautifully updated home offers a seamless blend of elegance and comfort, perfect for those seeking a spacious retreat from city life. This lovely home comes with 5 bedrooms plus bonus room that could easily be converted to a 6th, 3 bathrooms and an office with the primary en-suite on the main. AC for the summer heat. Partially fenced with equestrian potential. Enjoy Mt Baker Ski area, hiking, mountain biking, river rafting and fishing. Schedule your viewing today!

CHARMING 1926 Craftsman Bungalow time capsule! Sunny, fully fenced corner lot on a quiet street just steps from Broadway Park & Fountain District! 2 bed 1 full updated bath. Vintage details inside & out, original hardwood & fir floors, picture rails, built-ins, wooden corbels, fireplace, and welcoming front porch! Tastefully updated kitchen & pantry. 425sf unfinished basement w/egress door for another bed, bath, office? Large back & side yard with room for garden beds plus detached garage. Super clean, move-in ready w/space for D-ADU in place of existing garage buyer to verify. Leave your car behind with parks, shops, groceries, schools and Bellingham's downtown waterfront all nearby. A gardener's dream in a walker's paradise!

This charming, meticulously maintained, mid-century rambler is available for the 1st time in 60+ years. All new interior paint, fresh carpet, & refinished hardwood floors! A gardener's dream: enjoy hundreds of flowers in this remarkably large lot alongside blueberries, apple & fig trees, plus a brand-new front lawn! Expansive hardscaping; large private patio adjoins sidewalks surrounding both house & double car garage. Add a gate for a fully fenced yard. There is plenty of off-street parking, an electric vehicle charger & room for an RV. Dont miss the enormous attic w/ plumbing already brought up for a 2nd bathroom! Only one block to Parkview Elementary, Cornwall Park & the Rose Garden, mile to The Fountain District & St Joes Hospital.

Nestled in the highly sought-after Ridgemont neighborhood, this stunning home features a spacious living area with expansive windows framing mountain views and complemented by gas fireplaces on each level. The kitchen offers ample storage and opens onto a balcony, perfect for enjoying the outdoor views. Upstairs, the primary bedroom includes a 3/4 bathroom. Downstairs, discover a large bonus room, two bedrooms, a remodeled full bath, and a utility room. Outside, a west-facing deck provides sunset and bay views, while the backyard boasts a large storage shed and beautiful PNW foliage. Steps away from Ridgemont Park and close to trails and Galbraith Mountain. Don't miss out on this opportunity to embrace the Bellingham lifestyle!

Peaceful and serene property in a great location! Just 20 min from Bellingham and a short drive from the I-5 and the City of Blaine, this beautiful property has street frontage off Harvey Rd. A gravel driveway leads into a private, partially cleared and fully fenced oasis. Water and Electricity available in street. 4 parcels included in sale to equal just under an acre. Listed under assessed value! Perfect location for recreational use or to build your potential dream home! Verify w/county your plans and visit this beautiful property today!

Move-in ready home in this quiet Cordata neighborhood within walking distance of the new 25 acre recreation park with a splash Pad, playground, picnic area, walking trails and more. Welcome to your new home with newly painted kitchen, large master en-suite, with walk in shower, 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, back patio with fenced back yard and corner garden space. Double garage as well as parking outside. Tankless water heater. HOA mows the front lawn. Conveniently located with additional amenities nearby including the Bellingham Coop, Bellis Fair Mall, lots of shopping on Meridian St., Whatcom Community College and easy freeway access.

Think turn-key and easy living in this single-level home. The entire house has been updated: tile floors in the bathrooms, new paint, new trim, engineered hardwood floors throughout, expanded and updated kitchen, and for ultimate comfort, a new furnace and A/C were installed in 2021. With a low-maintenance yard, you can relax on the spacious back patio, or use it for RV parking. The 3-car garage provides ample storage for all your hobbies. Located in an excellent neighborhood on a quiet cul-de-sac with a private community park & walking trail. Five minutes to the mall, Barkley, Sunset, and I-5. This value for under $600K in Bellingham is hard to find! Welcome to your new home!

New construction! Estimated completion April 25. This brand new 3 bed, 1.75 bath offers durable vinyl plank flooring in main living spaces, comfortable carpets in the bedrooms and quartz countertops throughout. The vaulted ceilings create a light and airy feel inside. The primary bedroom has an attached en-suite with shower, while the full bathroom with shower and tub is accessible to the rest of the house. The exterior insulation has been upgraded beyond the building code requirements for better home temperature efficiency and noise dampening. Additionally, the interior walls have been insulated for noise dampening between rooms. The house is a blank canvas waiting for you to make it home!

Welcome to your new home with stunning views of Mt. Baker from the back deck! Step into this modern house featuring a custom-designed kitchen with farmhouse sinks, quartz counters, and plenty of natural light. Offering 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths, and energy-efficient mini-split heat pumps, along with solar panels, this home ensures both comfort and sustainability. Enjoy mornings on the deck overlooking nature, along with a fenced yard. This move-in ready gem backs to open space in a quiet neighborhood, close to Cordata Park, trails, medical facilities, shopping, and more!

Peaceful Edgemoor location, room to relax and enjoy. Sunny fenced backyard offers garden space, an entertainment deck, a patio wired for a hot tub, and room to play. Cozy up to the fireplace in the living room or stretch out in the family room. The lower level includes an office space. If you are looking for a home with lots of storage this is it, attic storage above the garage, loads of storage in the crawl space, and a special room off the garage for mowers and yard tools. Want to spend time in nature? You can. At the intersection of Chuckanut & Viewridge is access to 100 Acre Woods and the interurban trail. A few updates include a new roof in 2022, engineered wood flooring in the family room, exterior paint, and gutters.

Meticulously maintained, 3 bed, 2 bath rambler in King Mountain on dead end street. Step inside to massive kitchen featuring quartz counter tops, new stainless appliances, trash compactor, eating bar & pantry. Living area has ceiling fans, stone lined gas fireplace & engineered hardwood throughout. Primary bed w/primary bath beholds double vanities, jacuzzi & tiled shower tub & large walk-in closet. Live in comfort with LG W/D, instant hot water, A/C, gen hook up, & additional storage in crawl space/attic above garage. Step outside to trex deck w/privacy screen. Fully fenced backyard w/large graveled, low maintenance area, RV parking w/deeded alley access, & double gated drive through. Enjoy local park, easy access to amenities and more.

Experience the perfect fusion of urban living and spaciousness within walking distance to Barkley Village. The interior features modern updates including all bathrooms refreshed with new cabinets, countertops, and plumbing fixtures. The living room boasts a focal point stone fireplace, while the main level primary is equipped with built-in closets and luxe ensuite. Ample natural light streams in through added skylights, and the kitchen showcases newer appliances. The property's exterior has also undergone a transformation, with new siding, pavers, oversized deck, landscaping, & outdoor lighting. This property features a spacious shop, perfect for storage or hobbies - a rare find in the city! MOTIVATED SELLER BRING ALL OFFERS!

Welcome to South End Mobile Estates, a vibrant 55 and better Community nestled conveniently near Fairhaven Village's array of restaurants, shopping, and entertainment options. Step inside to discover this well-maintained home with a spacious living room and beautiful laminate wood floors, that flow seamlessly throughout the home. This thoughtfully designed 2-bedroom home features an updated bathroom w/walk-in shower. The updated kitchen offers ample storage options with a built-in buffet/china cabinet, perfect for storing all your essentials. With 2 backyard sheds providing additional storage and a covered patio overlooking the serene creek and nature trails, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty.

Nice buildable lot in Glenhaven with lake and mountain view! Cleared and ready for your new home! Mostly level and sloped in the front. Water and power available, no sewer, property will need a septic. Enjoy all the amenities that Glenhaven has to offer: clubhouse, seasonal pool, tennis court and 2 lakes for fishing and boating with battery powered motors.

Value in the land and outbuildings. Home is 2 bedrooms, 1 bath 840 sq ft and needs work. This nearly 20 acre, flat piece of property, with views of Mt Baker, has lots of possibilities. Several out buildings including a 64' X 52' heated shop, 24' X 70' lean-to, 24' X 100' shop, 20' X 50' covered parking, two 20' X 24' shops, 10' X 24' enclosed storage area, and another 16' X 70' shop. Water use for domestic, stock watering, and irrigation of a lawn and garden.

Nestled in a serene setting, this charming 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Situated on over 1 acre surrounded by open pastures and stunning mountain views, this property is just minutes from Everson. The home features mature landscaping, a large front deck perfect for enjoying the views, and a shed for additional storage. With newer siding and windows, a heat pump for efficient heating and cooling, and updated bathrooms and kitchen, this home is move-in ready and sure to impress.

This beautifully updated 5-bedroom home offers room for everyone in desirable Silver Beach! The thoughtful floor plan features a large living/dining room, perfect for gatherings, & a modern eat-in kitchen that seamlessly connects to an inviting family room. Step outside to a fully fenced backyard & wrap-around deck for indoor/outdoor living. Upstairs, the luxurious Primary Suite includes a spa-like bathroom & also four additional bedrooms with two sizable bathrooms. A conveniently located laundry room boasts two sets of washers and dryers! Recent updates include new LVP flooring, fresh interior paint, new lighting & plumbing fixtures, updated window coverings, & a new Trex deck. Move in & start enjoying your dream home!

Century Communities' popular Baylor Model Home is available at Horizon at Semiahmoo! Main floor has guest suite with adjacent bath, a gourmet kitchen w/refrigerator, large island and walk-in-pantry. Great room has a gas fireplace and a large bank of South-facing windows. Dining area has huge slider that opens onto a covered patio. Upstairs is the lavish primary suite that boasts a private covered deck, ensuite with dual vanities and a walk-in closet. 3 secondary bedrooms, a generous bonus room, full bath, and laundry room with cabinets, and washer and dryer complete the level. 2-bay garage with room for storage! Registration policy: Buyer Broker must accompany and personally register buyer at first visit.

This South Birch Bay lot is offered at a reduced price that considers the removal of a deteriorated cabin. The 651 square foot cabin, which has been unoccupied for years, is disconnected from electricity and is deemed uninhabitable at present. Water, sewer, and natural gas services are available. Please be advised that access is currently challenging due to vehicles blocking the end of Poplar Dr. Buyers are encouraged to commission a boundary survey and should consider the value of this property based on the land alone. Property unlikely to qualify for financing.

Come see this turn key rambler in the Belfern Estates, just minutes from Bellingham and Ferndale. Well maintained through out, the interior and kitchen were tastefully done to provide a comfortable and cozy living environment. Outside, youll find a large fenced yard perfect for pets, gardening, entertaining or just to relax and unwind privately with a covered patio and hot tub. Exterior features a newer roof installed with leaf filter gutters and solar panels to reduce your power bill. Don't miss this opportunity to own a home that combines sustainability, functionality, and tranquility.

Welcome to your dream home in the Birchwood neighborhood! Nestled on a fully fenced .83 acres, this beautifully remodeled 3 bedroom 1.5 bathroom craftsman offers modern living with a 1 bdrm 1 bathroom detached ADU apartment, a heated 24x30+ shop with a full bathroom, and 48 solar panels ensuring sustainability and energy efficiency. With a whole-house backup generator, and Air Conditioning, peace of mind comes standard. Embrace the outdoors with fruit trees, berries, raised garden beds, a greenhouse, and the lawn mower shed. Perfect for entertainers and nature lovers alike, this property awaits your personal touch with room to expand on the outdoors. Easy access to the Greenway Trail system and nearby parks. Don't miss out on this rare gem!

This Birch Bay waterfront gem features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and 1036 sq ft with low-bank access and beach rights. Step out your back door onto the best hard-packed sand flats in Washington State, with a perfect westerly-facing, unobstructed water view! Enjoy beach fires, sunsets, crabbing, clamming, and boating. Ideal for full-time living or Airbnb, this property is within walking distance of area restaurants, hair salons, beach trail systems, and the State Park.

Amazing creekfront condo with serene setting on edge of wooded hillside bordering Fishtrap Creek. Enjoy creek views! Spacious condo, 2 large bedrooms, 1 3/4 baths, great loft area for rec room, office or 3rd bdrm. Crown molding, lofty ceilings, 1 car garage & 1 off street parking. Walk to the fairgrounds, shopping or restaurants. Everything you could desire in this well appointed condo.

Immaculately maintained and upgraded 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Lynden with designer touches throughout. Open concept main floor living area with dining and kitchen areas. The kitchen boasts solid surface countertops, a large island, and stainless-steel appliances. The large light and bright primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. Convenient laundry on second floor with washer and dryer included. Beautifully landscaped minimal maintenance yard with covered front porch and upgraded deck and side yard. This home is extremely well-kept and is move-in ready!

Very rarely do homes become available in this quiet neighborhood, ideally located close to downtown and the world class recreational area of Galbraith Mountain and Lake Padden. This nearly 1, 600 square foot 4 bed 1.75 bath home features twin walk-in closets in the primary suite, an open main floor plan, ample parking, and fresh paint in and out, all complimented by a 3 year old roof. With a trailhead just a block away, you can unlock all the lifestyle opportunities that the area has to offer. Just 1.3 miles to Wade King Elementary and 2.9 to town, convenience doesnt come close to describing the location. Youll enjoy morning coffee on your deck, viewing a yard featuring organic apple, plum, and cherry trees, grapes and garden beds!

Delightful single-level home in Everson. Lot's of natural light throughout creates a warm & inviting atmosphere. Spacious kitchen w/ ample cabinet space & nice dining area. In addition to the inviting living room, there's a cozy family room with woodburning fireplace. Primary bedroom includes walk-in closet & 3/4 bathroom w/ private deck access. Outside, you'll find a manageable yard, along with a detached 3-car garage. One bay features an oversized door & plenty of space for your workshop needs. Plus, there's a lovely back deck complete with an above-ground pool, offering the ideal spot for outdoor enjoyment. Great location with walking distance to parks, shops & restaurants. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful home your own!

Beautiful 3+ acre property w/3 bd, 1 ba home & over 500 sq ft heated shop nestled in the hillside of Reese Hill. Gorgeous views of mother nature year-round - whether snow-dusted hills or bright colors of fall. Enjoy peace & quiet, yet you are only minutes from Sumas amenities down the hill and less than an hour to Mt. Baker & all it has to offer! Property has been well-utilized w/tons of fruit trees, garden areas, & heated shop for your hobbies. 1500 +/- sq ft home has cozy wood burning fireplace, great size kitchen, dining & living room - 3 bdrms inc flex space. All minutes from miles of great horse/biking trails & adjacent to state forest land. Great investment or vaca property!

Better then new construction, view property in an established neighborhood! Unlike new construction this home has all the window coverings in place along with a fully fenced backyard. The floor plan is wide open to the family room with a nice gas fireplace and includes 3 bedrooms with an office plus an upstairs bonus room. The elegant kitchen has a large island, soft close cabinets, granite counter tops, tiled backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. This home will be great for entertaining as it has a covered back patio and a very private backyard with a great view!

This well-maintained trailer sleeps 7 and can stay where it is or be towed to adventure! Featuring a spacious, sunlit dappled lot near the end of a quiet cul-de-sac and backing up to green space, you'll enjoy privacy and comfort. Additional storage is provided by the shed which could be used to expand space for guests, while the large fire pit & wood shed are perfect for outdoor gatherings. Trailer is easy to move when you're ready for an upgrade, too. Just 15 minutes from the base of Mount Baker as well as Silver Lake. The Glen amenities include two pools, a sauna, hot tub, basketball & tennis courts, two lodges, events & activities, 24/7 security and more. Zoned recreational limited to 120/nights per year occupancy. No rentals allowed.

Beautiful Home with partial lake views. Nestled on a quiet, sunny cul-de-sac this updated home has an inviting open floor plan with second living area and office. Custom, light filled kitchen with stunning granite island/countertops and stainless appliances. Bamboo flooring throughout the main level. Spacious primary bedroom includes a walk in closet and spa-like bathroom with radiant heated floors, double sinks and jetted tub. Relax in the fully fenced private backyard. Just a short walk to the neighborhood beach and Geneva elementary. One block to Waldorf school. Epic mountain biking/hiking trails just minutes from your door!

New roof is to be installed beginning 3/18/24~~The last expensive update to an exceptional residence! Main flr boasts lofty 9' ceilings, embracing an expansive open concept that's perfect for hosting gatherings. The flr plan features a versatile living rm w/elegant French doors that seamlessly connect to the more relaxed space. W/a gourmet kitchen & various dining options, this home is designed to be a hub of hospitality. Ascend the open stairs to the upper level, where you'll find 4 BRs including the primary suite w/recently updated bath w/freestanding soaking tub. Also upstairs, via a separate staircase for added privacy & versatility, is an oversized dbl bonus rm. Fully fenced yard w/sprinkler syst, shed. Garage w/tandom parking + shop.

Bellingham's finest street? You decide. This hard to find 1926 Tudor is an absolute South Hill charmer on South Forest Street. Original character abounds. Built-ins throughout. Meticulously maintained by one owner for almost 50 years. Excellent condition, mature landscaping. Newer roof, 3 decks overlooking Bellingham Bay. Beautiful library. Large finished basement. 2 garage bays off rear alley. Tons of storage. And more! Broad views to South, West and North of Bellingham Bay, islands and city. A must see!

Once in a lifetime opportunity to own a true, low bank, brand new lakefront home with all day sun exposure, dock, boat lift, flat grassy lawn and space enough for everyone! This irreplaceable home is impossible to describe completely here, but the main home is 5, 120 Sqft with walls of glass, 2 beds up plus cavernous primary suite and bonus room with ensuite bath, family rooms on both levels, office with ensuite bathroom on main, sauna, dog wash, mud room etc. In addition to the main home, a separate 1, 033 Sqft 2 bd 1 bth structure with an additional 1, 633 Sqft garage is tastefully located at back of property. Home is framed, roofed, plumbed, windows and exterior doors to be installed. Home is offered unfinished and will require completion.

Incredible investment opportunity awaits you! This ground level studio condo with 1 full bath and balcony is currently set up as a successful short term rental and is a turn key business :all bedding, furniture and supplies are included. This could easily be for personal use, friends and family, short term rental or all of the above for the year around adventures Mt Baker area has to offer. Condo amenities include private storage locker, exercise room, large game/rec room, free laundry and free parking! Located just 20 minutes to Silver Lake Park, 30 minutes to Mt Baker Ski area and 25 minutes to Heliotrope hiking trail, whatever outdoor activities bring you to the mountain this condo will be the perfect base camp.

Unique one level bungalow in an exquisite location just steps from Little Squalicum Park, the waterfront, and the future waterside boardwalk connector. You will love the peekaboo water views, large deck, stainless steel appliances, and wood floors. The home has an open floor plan that makes the home live large and efficient. Check out the newly tiled shower and tasteful finishes throughout. The 10, 000+ SF lot has previous county approval to convert the existing stick framed home into an accessory dwelling unit to a future home buyer could add to the property; a 2nd story home would offer great water views. For now, you will love the great off-street parking and beautifully designed storage and garage space in the powered container building.

The pinnacle of contemporary living on the west side of town! Crafted by Corban Construction, this 3 bed + office home embodies sophistication & style! Inviting ambiance on full display features 10' ceilings & an inviting 42 Kozy Heat gas fp framed by ship lap setting the tone for cozy evenings. Chef's dream kitchen! Quartz counters, soft-close cabinets, upgraded appliances, & a walk-in pantry. Large format tiles in bathrooms. Primary suite boasts a stunning frameless walk-in shower. Convenience meets tranquility w/ an insulated garage + sound walls ensuring peace. Experience year-round comfort w/ gas forced air + heat pump/AC & a H2O recirc pump. Covered patio invites outdoor relaxation amidst a huge 10, 454 sq ft lot w/ sprinkler system!

Stunning 2020 destination trailer located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Div 3 of the Glen at Maple Falls. You'll be wowed when you step inside! Theatre seating, solid surface counters w/ pendant lights, stainless steel sink & appliances & wood blinds are just some of the touches you'll discover. The bedroom features W/D hookups, there's central vac & a spacious loft upstairs for even more sleeping space. Outside there's a paver patio where you can spread out & soak up the sun in this bright, spacious lot just steps from the Gorge Trail which leads to the Nooksack River. Community amenities include two pools, parks, playgrounds, disc golf, tennis, Nooksack River access, 24/7 security & more. Limited to 120 days/year occupancy. No rentals.

Rare find in this beautiful low-bank Birch Bay waterfront condo where you can paddleboard or kayak off your own private beach! A 2-story, 3 bdrm, 3 bthrm at the desired Coast Haven Condominiums in the heart of the bay. Remodeled and updated kitchen & bathrooms with high-end finishes, cabinets, flooring, all new windows and coverings, & newly painted exterior. Open floor plan with living room & kitchen boasting a fabulous view opening up to your spacious new composite deck next to the beach! Also deck & stunning view from the upper primary bedroom. Covered carport parking with private storage. Best beach in Birch Bay for boating, crabbing, beachcombing, walking the new berm, close to restaurants, shops, amenities, PLUS amazing sunsets.

Discover serenity in this meticulously maintained 3 bed, 2 bath haven nestled on a tranquil dead-end street, bordered by vast open fields. Pride of ownership shines throughout this home, boasting an airy layout flooded with natural light. Retreat to the spacious primary suite, complete with a walk-in closet and peaceful separation from two additional bedrooms. Stay cozy by the wood-burning stove in the inviting family room. Outside, a picturesque fully fenced yard awaits, complemented by two convenient outbuildings for storage and wood. Embrace coastal living just moments from the beach, with recent upgrades including a new gas furnace in 2017 and a convenient carport addition. Your sanctuary awaits.

Two Story, 4 bdrm home in the desirable Barkley neighborhood, situated on a quiet cul-de-sac w/North facing views & a backyard that adjoins the treed 40-acre Northridge Park. Hardwood flrs on main level. Vaulted ceiling entry & living rm w/FP & picture windows overlooking the serene, wooded views. Island kitchen w/eating space, skylights, work area. Formal dining. Primary suite on the main level, dual sinks, tub, walk-in closet & separate shower rm. 3 rms up w/territory views. Includes central A/C, Honeywell full home generator & Tesla level-2 wall connector. Located minutes 2 Barkley Village & Lake Whatcom

This Sunnyland craftsman oozes charm & is completely dialed, just move in & enjoy! So many updates have been done while preserving the original look & feel of this 1920's cutie. The original fir flooring is still intact, along w/many of the original baseboards, doors & hardware. Updates include a ductless heat pump, new roof, updated electrical, new windows, gas fireplace & a completely updated kitchen. Updated bathroom w/ walk-in shower, Marmoleum flooring, new cabinets & countertops. Fresh paint inside & out, huge utility/mud room & fully fenced magical back yard with endless opportunities & a 40 year old grafted cherry tree! Large detached garage w/alley access & storage. Minutes to Cornwall & Broadway parks, TJ's, breweries, & more.

Nestled within a serene expanse of mature forest, this very clean and well-maintained rambler is only minutes from town and amenities. Expansive windows frame picturesque views of your very own tranquil and secluded 5+ acres. 2 bedroom and 2 full bath home offers vaulted ceilings, lots of natural light, and an open layout that's perfect for entertaining and relaxing. Huge kitchen with tons of storage/built-ins and room for everyone. Oversized primary bedroom boasts extra closet space and a huge ensuite. Additionally, there are 2 seasonal creeks, a duck pond, orchard, massive oak trees and wildlife. This property must be seen to be appreciated.

Experience effortless living in this fantastic low-maintenance single-level home. Situated in the serene Silver Beach neighborhood, tucked away on a tranquil cul-de-sac just minutes from shopping, schools, Lake Whatcom, parks and trails. This gem rests on a generous private .29 acre lot adorned with a garden shed and mature landscaping, bordering city-owned greenspace alive with songbirds. Meticulously maintained, featuring hardi-plank siding, energy-efficient HVAC. Wired for security and a generator for peace of mind. Trex decking invites outdoor relaxation. Inside is a fantastic floorplan, custom Hunter Douglas window coverings, renovated baths, a sunny office and spacious kitchen. Welcome to a lifestyle where every day feels effortless.

Build your dream home, bring in a manufactured home or use as a weekend getaway in Sandy Point Heights! 5th Wheel and storage container are included in sale. Water, Sewer and Power are already on this partially fenced and private lot ready for your home plans. Spend your weekends in the RV & BBQing on the large deck until you build your dream home with the potential for water views on the second story. Just a short walk to Lummi Bay, the community golf course, clubhouse, swimming pool & sport courts. A quick drive to the community marina with a boat launch for some of the best Dungeness crabbing in the NW!

Discover effortless living in this single-level residence nestled in a highly sought-after neighborhood. Enjoy the privacy of light-filled living and dining areas, complemented by a kitchen boasting abundant cabinets and expansive counter space. Retreat to spacious bedrooms and take advantage of the practicality of a laundry room. Outside, the large lot offers a landscaped oasis complete with 2 outdoor buildings, ensuring privacy and tranquility. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your perfect home sweet home.

Nestled beside Semiahmoo's scenic 17th green, this custom-built single-story home embodies luxury living at its finest. Built in 2021, this home boasts impeccable craftsmanship & an array of high-end features. Inside, spacious interiors are bathed in natural light, offering panoramic views of the golf course. Step onto the elevated deck for year-round outdoor enjoyment, complete with infrared heaters for added comfort. Privacy awaits in the guest en-suite, while the versatile 3rd bedroom doubles as a convenient home office. Thoughtful design ensures accessibility throughout, while the 3-car garage provides ample storage space. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the perfect blend of elegance and practicality in this must-see residence.

Located in a cul-de-sac, this Keystone trailer boasts rich wood tones throughout making for a cozy atmosphere. It has everything you'll need for a comfortable home away from home. Outside, enjoy the nature by taking advantage of the beautiful greenspace, or sitting around the campfire. A shed also sits on the property for additional or larger storage items. There is plenty of room to have fun on this lot, and make it uniquely yours! The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouses, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Welcome Home to your sanctuary in the city! This 4 bed 2.5 bath rambler is located at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac with direct access to Whatcom Falls Park and the Bellingham trail system. The home lives light and bright with tons of windows and several glass sliding doors that lead out to the fully fenced backyard that feels like a private retreat. The kitchen is the heart of the home and has been thoughtfully updated with quartz countertops, black stainless appliances, and an additional butlers kitchen and pantry. Newer paint and luxury vinyl flooring throughout the home provides a modern move in ready appeal. Ample off-street parking, as well as a large oversized garage that is equipped to fit an RV, round out this amazing home.

Dream Kitchen in this spacious 1820 square foot, one- level rancher. Home has been completely remodeled with new laminate floors, paint, light fixtures and more. The dream kitchen has all new stainless-steel appliances, quartz counter tops, decorator lighting fixtures and glass doors that lead directly out to a patio. The hallways and doorways are extra large in width. The Master bedroom features a walk-in closet, large en-suite bathroom and French doors that lead out to its own private patio. There is a separate garage and workshop (with electrical power). This home sits on 63' x 135' lot however, if you would like more room, the lot next door to this home may be available for purchase.

Nestled amidst the serene beauty of Lummi Island, this enchanting cabin offers a tranquil escape from everyday life. Surrounded by towering evergreens and overlooking the sparkling waters of the Salish Sea, this retreat embodies the essence of Pacific Northwest charm. Step inside to discover a warm and inviting interior, open-concept living space, vaulted ceilings with exposed wood beams, second level loft, all framed by large windows with breathtaking views of the surrounding nature. Outside, the wonders of Lummi Island await. Whether you're hiking through lush forest trails, fishing pristine shorelines, or simply strolling along the beach, there's no shortage of outdoor activities to enjoy. Come experience the magic of Lummi Island!
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: Views as nice as you will find anywhere! Sunsets, Sound and Bay Views. Islands, private beach, heated indoor swimming pool and exercise room, tennis courts, lots of parking and below rental cap! This END unit has windows on 3 sides is in very good decorative order and had new kitchen appliances in last 18 months. Living area with cozy fireplace. Two private decks to enjoy. Live like you are on vacation all year round! This unit is in phase 2 and is sprinklered for fire protection.

Beautiful 2014 square foot home nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac in a prime neighborhood steps from Ridgemont Park. This 3-bed, 2.5 bath split-level home with hardwood flooring offers 3 beds upstairs, a vaulted ceiling living room + a large walkout basement. Private fenced backyard with beautiful landscaping along with a garden shed and lots of space for entertaining. Kitchen w/ stainless appliances, updated cabinets, and adjoining dining room and kitchen nook. West-facing 500 square foot deck and hot tub with views of sunsets and Sehome hill. Home has 2 gas fireplaces, A/C and a new furnace. The 2-car garage includes a home office space. Close to Lake Padden, downtown, WWU, and I-5.

Must see Everson area farm house. House is 1964 sq ft with 3 bedrooms and 1 3/4 baths. Some recent upgrades include new roof, exterior paint, new carport roof and new laminate flooring throughout. Home sits on just over half an acre with fruit trees, garden space, a 20x30 yard shed and a fenced backyard. Come see all the potential this home has today.
